---
export const prerender = true;
import SwissLayout from "../../../components/SwissLayout.astro";
---

<SwissLayout title="Privacy Policy — Alpha Digital Agency" description="Privacy Policy for Alpha Digital Agency Indonesia. How we collect, use, and protect your data." currentPage="">

  <section class="pt-28 md:pt-40 pb-16 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-emerald-dark dark:text-white mb-8">Privacy <span class="text-primary">Policy</span></h1>

    <div class="prose prose-emerald dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-dark dark:text-white">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly: name, email, phone number, and messages through our contact forms. We also collect analytics data (page views, sessions) through Google Analytics and Cloudflare.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-dark dark:text-white">2. How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>We use your information to respond to inquiries, provide our services, improve our website, and send relevant communications. We never sell your data.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-dark dark:text-white">3. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use essential cookies for website functionality and analytics cookies (Google Analytics) to understand usage. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-dark dark:text-white">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use: Google Analytics (analytics), Cloudflare (hosting & security), Google Workspace (email). Each has its own privacy policy.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-dark dark:text-white">5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>Contact form submissions and analytics data are retained for as long as needed to provide our services. You can request deletion by contacting us.</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-dark dark:text-white">6. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy inquiries: <a href="mailto:daniel@alphadigitalagency.id" class="text-primary hover:underline">daniel@alphadigitalagency.id</a></p>

    </div>
  </section>

</SwissLayout>
